          <p><strong>Yechim:</strong> Click yoki Payme app'ida "Sozlamalar → Mening kartam → Identifikatsiyani o'tish" bosqichini bajarish. 5–10 daqiqalik passport rasmi va selfie yuborish — keyin limit avtomatik 5–10 mln so'mga oshadi.</p>

